description:
Pick a Plan – Earn Rewards – Live Better

Earn points, for healthier living and claim rewards. Allow health and wellness professionals to monitor your progress by booking online appointments from a range of health and wellness experts. These experts will have self-management plans that you can follow on a daily or weekly basis.

To help ourselves maintain a healthy lifestyle, we need the information and tools to do so. Whether you want to manage an existing health condition or just want some help to improve your lifestyle, Health Fabric is where you need to be! Access a library of health and wellbeing plans.  Some plans have daily tasks, and if the user completes their daily tasks, they earn points towards certain rewards. These plans can be complemented with access to health and wellness experts that provide virtual consultations via the app. Whatever your goal may be Health Fabric is equipped to help in a way that suits you. Putting you in control of your Health and wellbeing.

What do the users think?
“I recently started running. I’m going to use ‘MyHealthFabric’ to kick start my fitness plan and track my progress” – MyHealthFabric User
“I have been a Type 1 diabetic since I was one and a half. I control my diabetes with four insulin shots a day. Previously I found it really difficult to remember to take my insulin shots before or after meals. The App is really helpful reminding me when to take my shots. It’s also useful to track my blood sugar before and after exercise. The library access gives me links to websites and direct information instead of having to search through the internet just to find one useful website. IT’S BRILLIANT!” - Becky Cash
“I’m using ‘MyHealthFabric’ for inspiration and motivation” – MyHealthFabric User
“I’m using ‘MyHealthFabric’ to help me balance my university commitments with my social life to reduce my stress levels.” – Jess Palm
“Being an Asthmatic I’ve struggled to do high intensity exercise. Other Apps I’ve used give you High Intensity workouts which haven’t worked for me. This App is brilliant because I can create my own fitness regime with a mixture of high and low intensity. I don’t feel I need to take my inhaler as much anymore. Something as simple as this will benefit me for the rest of my life.” – MyHealthFabric User
